name: yTOFU
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
YTOFU token smart contract
Token generated through ySOY +BNB +LP mill this token has no defined Supply.
For this reason ysoychain will burn tokens, decreasing the amount of tokens in circulation, making ysoychain tokens scarce in the market and increasing their trading value.
